WEBVTT

00:03:57.718 --> 00:04:01.110
So this is a typical day,
12-18 hours, non-stop

00:04:01.134 --> 00:04:03.296
capturing the entire day unfold.

00:04:04.290 --> 00:04:07.266
One of the things that's great
is I love to people-watch.

00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:08.703
And trust me when I tell you,

00:04:08.727 --> 00:04:10.925
this is the greatest seat
in the house to have.

00:04:12.226 --> 00:04:15.330
But this is really how I go about
creating these photographs.

00:04:15.785 --> 00:04:19.497
So once I decide on my view
and the location,

00:04:19.521 --> 00:04:22.680
I have to decide where day begins
and night ends.

00:04:22.704 --> 00:04:24.846
And that's what I call the time vector.

00:04:25.476 --> 00:04:28.759
Einstein described time as a fabric.

